// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1728 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a1d7a8a3-416b-5b72-9600-bc4b340bd196

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:12.04*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
